/*! @file
@brief README of the directory pseudo/src

@dir
@brief Contains the source of the pseudo and atom programs

@details
Changes as of Fri Jun 28 2013 by Alex Willand

- modules in pseudo.f90 with descriptions of the relevant variables
- much shorter dummy argument lists for amoeba, ppack, penalty, gatom
- radgrid.f and crtvh.f are ported to f90
- labels, gotos and capital letters are widely eliminated
- indention mostly adjusted to 3 spaces per level and 5 for line continuation
- pawpatch routines (including gatom_mofied) are left unmodified and should be tested 

*/
